{"_path":"/travel/v005","_dir":"travel","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"香港-景點匯總","description":"香港旅遊 - 景點美食","image":null,"sequence":5,"category":"2.香港旅遊","link":null,"head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口 - 社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"旅行導遊"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-09-11T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"香港旅遊-景點匯總"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"香港旅遊 - 景點匯總"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"小紅書 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/668bc4360000000025007986?xsec_token=ABMZ8qbpfAONaPJ8CPXIcOpr_P2Ub2jjF_EZ1urS4cviM=&xsec_source=pc_search&source=unknown"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"香港必去九大景點"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"klook "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.klook.com/zh-TW/experiences/list/hong-kong-tours/c2-cate9/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"香港熱門觀光行程"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"坚尼地城"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n位于港岛的西边，附近不仅有香港大学 、西营盘等街拍地点，还有独特的日落海景\n我们沿着叮叮路线一路打卡，收获了不少的宝藏街景\n搭配富士相机 ，妥妥的网红拍照"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"太平山"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n来香港一定要来太平山\n傍晚的时候可以欣赏到日落城市逐渐亮起灯光的过程\n晚上夜景也是更加璀璨夺目我们刚好赶在太阳快落山去 既能看到夜景也能看到日落 超赞的！！！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"海港城"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n走到海港城的网红大楼梯、笑脸装置 还有打卡了好多咖啡店 很出片的地方 拍出来的海也绝美"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"落日飞车"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n这是我来香港特想体验的巴士\n坐上那一刻 整个人都是自由的 在太阳下山时看到日落搭配沿路的风景 真的是一切烦恼全部消失"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"香港博物馆"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n做为一名艺术生的我，我真的很喜欢去博物馆艺术馆\n直到进去香港博物馆，看到那些展品 艺术品 真的是非常的震撼！！！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"香港迪士尼"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n港迪真的是我玩下来体验感很好的一次了！！！\n无需排长队和早起，港迪的夏日花车真的好绝还有魔雪奇缘世界，仿佛走进了电影里，真的是太梦幻了！！！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"维多利亚港"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n维港真的好美！ 它是世界上繁忙的港口之一。\n维多利亚港的夜景也是尤为迷人，真的不要错过每晚的灯光秀！！！超棒的！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"油麻地庙街"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n感受香港地道的烟火气 逛了一天，来感受香港的夜生活 整条街上布满了各类地摊与美食小店。超多港式小食咖喱鱼蛋、牛杂、煎釀三宝、碗仔翅等。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"铜锣湾"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n香港的心脏地带 想要体验香港的繁华，铜锣湾是不可错过的目的地。这里汇聚了世界各地的购物者，美食家和探险者，是香港的繁华之源。在铜锣湾 尽量避免周末和节假日，这样可以避开人流高峰。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"小紅書 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/66d96b970000000012011ea9?xsec_token=ABEHYB3-vYCfXZ-Q9y1CyHpndrWOm6W9tkJ0bHEKaX4Bo=&xsec_source=pc_search&source=unknown"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"香港一日遊"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"v005-04.jpeg","src":"/images/travel/v005-04.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"v005-02.jpeg","src":"/images/travel/v005-02.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"香港旅遊-景點匯總","depth":2,"text":"香港旅遊 - 景點匯總"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:travel:v005.md","_source":"content","_file":"travel/v005.md","_extension":"md"}